Title: Extension packages: Fix error on usage of "mkp show"
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1660554659
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0p10

If the command "mkp show" was used with mkp files like "my_mkp.mkp", the error
"Cannot open package my_mkp.mkp: I/O operation on closed file" occurred.
